page.name: Whale Of A Good Time!
page.description: This is a special quest where the monsters adjust themselves to your level! But you all know that from the FIRST time we ran it. NOWWWW, we are using it to test the quest reward...you will get a "Stackable Item". It stacks up to 5. Let us know on the Bug forums if you encounter any bugs.
